 Destructor let go of waspinator. He waled up to the base and lowered the 
shields by voice code..he walked over to famine.."Sir Kit Kat has adviced to 
have Megatron on the council." Destructor just cried out in 
frustration..."Why does she keep doing these foolish things. Why does she not 
counsult her own ordered advisor. " he walked into the base and the horsemen 
followed. In search of Kit kat.
